Muriel Robin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muriel_Robin 0 Muriel Robin is a French actress. She won an International Emmy Award for Best Actress in 2007 and received a nomination for a César Award in 2001 and six nominations for a Molière Award. Muriel_Robin is a_French_actress .
